ABOUT TEH

THE ENTREPRENEURS HUB

Is one of a kind to bring in the growth for the entrepreneurs through various kind, we help all the entrepreneurs to grow through networking, reference, help each one in building the brand, marketing and promotion. Our goal is to grow and help each other grow where we all can reach our respective goals, we want to be part in each one's sector in growing the business. We are in Pan India level growing where we help the start-up companies and small-scale business people. Women empowerment is our main goal to help them reach the market space through our organisation and help them build their business, most of the women entrepreneurs lack in connectivity and don't know how to move forward thus We come into picture to help them. We are into B2B and B2C where we do peer in the business in binding each one and help in branding and marketing and promotion, we provide lead generation to help the business grow and reach to the market through our website. We lend helping hand for all the entrepreneurs either be the start-up or the established company or small-scale business people. We are into 3 verticals Business, Events and Women's Club

{/* Uncomment the following code if needed */}
  • Business: We help all the entrepreneurs to grow through networking, branding, promotion, and marketing.
  • Events: We do events to do branding, marketing, and promotion for our own company. We invite other entrepreneurs who would be interested in joining hands in branding, marketing, and promotion through these events, and we both can travel together successfully.
  • Women's Club: We want to bring in the ladies from all segments, either homemakers, working women, or businesswomen, to come forward to share their thoughts and be themselves. In the Women's Club, we help all the ladies to interact, greet, meet, and build their networking, socializing, and business. We provide workshops for the ladies free of cost where it can help them in building their confidence level and overall well-being.
  • We are looking to hire people who can work with us in this development of helping each other in all these 3 verticals and let's all grow our organization. We have a very good business opportunity where you can earn up to 20% just by referring the members and help us grow our organization in which you will be building a team that helps you to grow and the organization as well.


Founder
Mrs. Sharada Manoranjan

 Mrs. Sharada Manoranjan Home maker turned entrepreneur have come a long way in this journey with the vision of creating a platform for the entrepreneurs, my organisation is called The Entrepreneurs Hub (TEH) home maker turned entrepreneurs who are lacking in networking and referrals. In covid period many business ppl we're affected without any networking and connections and myself among them one was desperate and wanted to do something and got this idea of starting this organization for benefits of startup and women entrepreneurs who do business from there respective homes. Thus this organization was born.

Founder
Dr. Mamtha Sudhakar

 Dr. Mamtha Sudhakar BEHM (ACU) Dr. Mamtha Sudhakar, An electro Homeopathy doctor with 15 years of experience in various therapies Acupressure Masters Reiki and Vaastu correction. She has also wide knowledge and experience in other Startup Interior Designing Ayurvedic products. Has been awarded by some of important forums in Bangalore as an leading Women Enterpreneur. Her thoughts and ideas have helped many for the self developing Individual in many of the Women forums with a great social responsibility to empower the women and also men.

Director

 Engineer by profession working in a private sector joined hands with this organisation The Entrepreneurs Hub in development, moral support and helping in ideas of developing the business strategy.
